    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 Supra Turbo is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. The sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six delivers linear power through the sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This unit retains its factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, providing exceptional lateral grip and high-speed stability. Recent maintenance includes a full timing belt service and fresh fluid cycles for the intercooler and braking systems. The chassis remains rigid, and the forced induction system holds consistent boost across the rev range. An honest, mechanically robust icon ready for the open road.",
