      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the E46 chassis, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive Double VANOS overhaul and documented rear subframe reinforcement, addressing critical platform-specific concerns. The suspension retains its sharp response with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the car\u2019s signature 50/50 weight distribution is fully utilized. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain integrity is excellent, supported by a recently performed valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for performance and tactile feedback.",
